# web-main Rules (kealee.com — Fully Public)

## Auth State
web-main has ZERO auth state.
- No `useUser()` calls
- No `getSession()` calls
- No portal subdomain links in any CTA
- No conditional rendering based on auth

## Routing
- "Build your project" CTA → `/concept` (public intake) — NEVER app.kealee.com
- "Sign in" → `/auth/sign-in` (existing members only)
- Milestone Pay → primary nav item

## Project Paths (3 types only)
1. Design + Permits
2. Permits Only
3. Contractor Only

## Pricing
NEVER hardcode prices in components or pages.
Import ALL prices from `packages/core-rules/src/pricing.ts`.

## Product Pages
25+ product pages live in `apps/web-main/src/app/products/[slug]/page.tsx`
Each must be fully public, server-rendered, prices from core-rules.

## AskAnythingBar
- Client component (needs useState)
- On submit: POST to `/api/concept` with `{ query: string }`
- Show loading skeleton during API call
- Mobile-first responsive, Tailwind only
